dc_title_s: Map showing oyster house lots at West Creek, Ocean County and depth of creek at low water
dc_description_s: This is a blueprint of the oyster house lots on West Creek including the names of the property owners.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Map describes West Creek as in Ocean County. There is also a West Creek in Cape May County (also called Westecunk Creek). Ocean County has a town called West Creek but there is also a creek named West Creek in Cape May County. The map shows the creek West Creek and says it is in Ocean County.
